elvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;" /><span style="color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; float: none; display: inline;">　　</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">3．术语和定义<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />　　3.1<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />　　电子合同 electronic contract</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;" /><span style="color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; float: none; display: inline;">　　电子合同是平等主体的自然人、法人、其他组织之间以数据电文为载体，并利用电子通信手段设立、变更、终止民事权利义务关系的协议。本标准推荐订约双方采用电子签名并使用符合本标准的订约方式订立合同。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', He