vetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; float: none; display: inline;">　　</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">5.2 信息公示</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;" /><span style="color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; float: none; display: inline;">　　电子合同订立系统应当在网站主页面醒目位置披露设立人的名称、地址、工商登记信息、税务登记信息、经营性网站许可信息、联系电话、电子邮件地址等，并公示系统业务说明，包括合同订立、谈判、签名和存储规则、系统安全保障措施、系统运营管理制度和相关风险提示等内容。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;" /><span style="color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; float: none; display: inline;