ca, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; float: none; display: inline;">　　电子合同的完整储存信息应当包括合同内容、签约时间、合同订立各方主体信息、电子签名信息等。订约人可随时在订约系统中查阅自己签订的合同信息。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;" /><span style="color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; float: none; display: inline;">　　存储服务商可应电子合同订立人的请求，对其合同谈判过程提供存储服务。储存后的电子合同能够应缔约人的请求进行在线查看和下载。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;" /><span style="color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; float: none; display: inline;">　　</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">8.2 电子合同查询</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;" /><span style="color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; float: none; display: inline;">　　电子合同订立各方可以通过在线和离线两种方式查询电子合同第三方存储服务商保存的电子合同。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;" /><span style="color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; float: none; display: inline;">　　利用在线方式查询电子合同，应利用电子签名制作数据进入电子合同第三方存储服务商网站，并按照存储服务商规定的操作程序查询。</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font-size: 18px;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #262626; font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Liberation Sans', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif; font